{"tid":1602348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［西貢］需用拐枚工黨常委被四白衣人圍毆 現正接受手術治療","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T11:24:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1bda8c80e76e8ad325305a27d2a1849b31bcf4a2","tid":1602348,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"西貢發生傷人案，下午4時許，工黨常委兼職工盟工會教育幹事何偉航途經萬年街23號對開時，突遭4名白衣人持棍圍毆，附近一名女街坊阻止時亦被打傷，兇徒事後四散。警員接報到場，將何偉航及受傷女街坊一併送院治理。警方正在現場調查，追緝4名與案有關男子。<br />\n<br />\n讀者阿芬事發時經過上址，她指何偉航被白衣人圍毆，形容兇徒棍棍打頭，「直頭係想攞命」，附近一間食肆老闆上前阻止時亦被扑傷。愛協獸醫及姑娘事後將傷者帶入獸醫診所內治理。阿芬指，何偉航早前曾在區內搞放影會，不排除有人想於區選滅聲，令參選人退選。<br />\n<br />\n工黨立法會議員張超雄證實何偉航遇襲，他指何偉航曾患骨癌，其後變長短腳，出入需要用拐杖，但兇徒照用硬物施襲，出手狠毒，何用手擋格時致骨折受傷，現時須接受手術治理。張超雄表示，懷疑包括鄺俊宇在內的連串遇襲事件或與黑幫有關，他批評警方執法不力，令香港瀰漫一片白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190929/60098050?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60098050%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLe9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=033241ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60098050%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=189d543d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190929/60098050?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6c3430bce89868ca1dd078e73a88840436340668","tid":1602348,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.faceboo